To install the Michael Theys date calendar dialog.

1.  TSO RECEIVE the RCQXMIT member.
2.  Copy panels  RCQDATE and RCQDATE$ to an ISPPLIB dataset.
3.  Copy clist   RCQDATEC to a SYSPROC dataset.
4.  Copy message RCQMO00 to an ISPMLIB dataset.

To run the Michael Theys date calendar dialog:

1.  Select 7 on the "Options" pull-down menu.

       Memlist  Functions  Options  Special  Defaults  Help
     ------------------- +--------------------------------------+
                         |    1. Subcommand Selection...        |
     Command ===>        |    2. PDS Processing Options         |
    Enter an ISPF comman |    3. IBM System Information         |
     - DSN=AD.FILE182.PD |    4. Dataset Usage                  |
     CMD  NAME     DATA  |    5. Change Datasets                |
          $$$DOC         |    6. Change Dataset Menu...         |
          $$$RCQDT       |    7. Michael Theys Date Calendar... |
          #PDSTBL        +--------------------------------------+

    - OR -

2.  Enter the RCQDATE extended subcommand.
